{"tid":671501,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"（android 7)點先可以改返做「台灣規範」既正體字？","createTime":"2018-05-20T07:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T08:56:44.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb17044bead5b36b52b07dca82e94168804372b","tid":671501,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cd8ad178cf8fd7325a4d7c61539083713b5acc","tid":671501,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:18:10.000Z","msg":"自問自答先：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下載 Android 手機字體 (iphone請甭下載)<br />\n請先到 設定 / 安全性 ，勾選 未知來源，才能安裝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣楷體：<a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/twkaiapk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Ftwkaiapk&d=C29PdPJit049SSA3pMxrJgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7a7ce876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tinyurl.com/twkaiapk</a><br />\n台灣宋體：<a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/twsongapk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Ftwsongapk&d=C29PdPJit049SSA3pMxrJgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2cb102da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tinyurl.com/twsongapk</a><br />\n詳細操作說明：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/DmisiF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FDmisiF&d=C29PdPJit049SSA3pMxrJgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2d986b5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/DmisiF</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps.三星手機阻擋第三方軟體安裝字型，只允許下載他自己市場內的1個免費字體與多個付費字體(但無法呈現本土語言漢字)，若該系統有修正，三星使用者再回覆一下喔。<br />\nps2.Sony與其他廠牌的可以換字體嗎？也請回覆一下喔。"},{"pid":"92ba4353b1845ce43ceb08ddeaa0e5b9339aba09","tid":671501,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"蘋方-港"}]}